<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka gitloh netna cheng sawpthienna di'n,
 Kalvari kross ah Isu kikhen den;
 Angelte'n a en ui mak a sau hi,
 Migilo kei di'n, A kipumpiek na.

[V2]
 Aw hehpihna mak! Aw tatna mantam,
 Ka gitloh beihna'n man lopi A pie'i;
 Chanchinpha genun, Hukdamna manbei,
 Gilo kei di'n hehpihna mak ahi.

[V3]
 2. Ka gitlohna cheng Isu'n A pawtai,
 Ka tatna man kim athawn in A pie'i;
 Ka gitlohna cheng kross chungah A puo'i,
 Gilo kei di'n hehpihna mak ahi.

[V4]
 3. Linglukhuk khuksak in a chiehpih ui,
 Lungkham ni'n Luguh munlam a tun ui;
 Khuo ahungthim a micheng in a muu,
 Migilo kei di'n A kipumpiek na.

[V5]
 4. A luong a siel ui Jospeh than thak ah,
 Khetden Lalpa chuh Hukdam di'n A hat;
 A hinna A pie'i, kei ka hin theih na'n,
 Gilo kei di'n hehpihna mak ahi.</lyrics>
<title>WONDERFUL LOVE</title>
<hymn_number>113</hymn_number>
</song>